<p><img src="/sites/all/themes/dul_master_2013/images/devillogo-60pct-60.png" alt="Reading Devil" title="Reading Devil" width="60" height="105" style="float: right;">This website serves as the place to begin the process of entering content for the new Drupal-powered Duke University Library website. &nbsp;</p>

<p>To log into the website, please click the "Sign on with your NetID" link, located in the <strong>Duke NetID Login</strong> box on the right side of the page.</p>

<p>The content on this website will be migrated to the final, production website in time for the big "launch" in October!</p><p>In the event you experience log-in difficulties, <strong><a href="contact/Website-feedback">please send a note to Derrek Croney</a></strong> and he will provide quick resolution.</p>
